巴勒斯坦问题回到「两国方案」轨道。 王毅强调，巴勒斯坦问题根源在于巴勒斯坦人民的合法权益未能得到恢复和保障，解决这一问题的出路是落实「两国方案」。中方从今天起出任本月安理会轮值主席，我们将与各方尤其是阿拉伯国家加强协调，主持公道，凝聚共识，为实现冲突降级、保护平民、缓解人道局势、恢复和平进程作出不懈努力。王毅同阿曼外交大臣巴德尔通电话：中方出任本月安理会轮值主席，将与阿拉伯国家加强协调，主持公道"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4a22f8e69284e90dd778a2c89b964466_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "395 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/628771107"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI0cb5mdPo+et3EAMaCTEwMjAwNTU4NCDj7YuqBjAAOLcCQANyCTYyODc3MTEwN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1698905260.271886", "card_id": "Q_621461019", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 91}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "著名开悟者萨古鲁说过：「人体需要的是休息，而不是睡眠不要试图提高自己的睡眠质量」如何理解？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8972ed1aac6d324e34d8268e87b59dde_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "164 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/621461019"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI0cb5mdPo+et3EAMaCTEwMDM4MjE4NyDKhfqnBjAAOO4BQARyCTYyMTQ2MTAxOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1698905260.272575", "card_id": "Q_628653943", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 199}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "也门胡塞武装发表声明证实，通过弹道导弹等，对以色列多个目标进行了大规模打击，这将对中东产生何种影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "也门胡塞武装发表声明证实，通过弹道导弹和无人机，对以色列多个目标进行了大规模打击"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-cae9eb0e9fbd8fea34769c3bdc53c561_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, 